text:
What’s the mean bill length, by species?

penguins |&gt;
  group_by(species) |&gt;
  summarise(mean_bill_length = mean(bill_length_mm, na.rm = TRUE))

# A tibble: 3 × 2
  species   mean_bill_length
  &lt;fct&gt;                &lt;dbl&gt;
1 Adelie                38.8
2 Chinstrap             48.8
3 Gentoo                47.5
